Package: writetfl
Title: Standardized Table, Figure, and Listing Output for Clinical Trial Reporting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides composable PDF page layout for exporting tables, figures,
    and listings (TFLs) with the standardized formatting required for clinical
    trial reporting and regulatory submissions. Pages are divided into header,
    caption, figure, footnote, and footer sections with independently controlled
    spacing, typography, and separator rules. Layout dimensions are computed
    dynamically from font metrics using the grid graphics system. Suitable for
    any context requiring reproducible, precisely controlled page layout.
